        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【最疼的皮肤病！#3类高风险人群更要警惕带状疱疹#】专家表示，#三分之一人群一生中会患带状疱疹#，而年龄是带状疱疹最重要的危险因素。据统计，中国50岁以上人...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【最疼的皮肤病！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%233%E7%B1%BB%E9%AB%98%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E6%9B%B4%E8%A6%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%23&amp;extparam=%233%E7%B1%BB%E9%AB%98%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E6%9B%B4%E8%A6%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#3类高风险人群更要警惕带状疱疹#</span></a>】专家表示，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%9A%E6%82%A3%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%9A%E6%82%A3%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#三分之一人群一生中会患带状疱疹#</span></a>，而年龄是带状疱疹最重要的危险因素。据统计，中国50岁以上人群每年新发带状疱疹约156万人，年龄越大越容易患病，病情也更严重。此外，糖尿病、慢性肾脏疾病等慢性病患者，患病风险增加24%到41%；自身免疫疾病患者，如类风湿关节炎、系统性红斑狼疮等，患病风险是一般人群的2.3倍到4倍。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%2322%E5%B2%81%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E6%82%A3%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%23&amp;extparam=%2322%E5%B2%81%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E6%82%A3%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E7%96%B1%E7%96%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#22岁女生长期熬夜患带状疱疹#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YlrmFQ" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
